These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, australian, french, indonesian
4 different pets are kept: cat, bird, pony, goat
1. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the nigerian##1
3. the australian is on the left or right of the french##3
4. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
5. the indonesian is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
6. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
7. the australian is somewhere between the nigerian and the owner of the bird##7
8. the australian and the owner of the goat have the same parity positions##9
9. the french and the owner of the cat have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | australian | french     | indonesian |
| Pet           | pony   | goat     | bird | cat  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, soy-milk, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, collecting, gardening, camping
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is camping and the person drinking juice have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##8
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
6. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
7. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
8. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | water     | soy-milk    | milk | juice    |
| Hobby      | fishing | collecting | gardening      | camping |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, papaya, asparagus, blueberry
1. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person eating asparagus##5
2. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
7. the person eating watermelon is not to the left of the person eating papaya##8
8. the person drinking sprite and the person eating papaya have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | sprite    | almond-milk   | juice    | hot-chocolate  |
| Food       | papaya | blueberry | watermelon | asparagus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, electrician, manager, scientist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, r&b, electronic, folk
1. the fan ambient is the electrician##1
2. the fan r&b is on the right of the fan electronic##1
3. the fan r&b is somewhere to the left of the electrician##5
4. the fan folk is on the left or right of the manager##3
5. the fan r&b is on the left of the fisherman##1
6. the scientist and the fan folk have the same parity positions##9
7. the manager is on the left or right of the fisherman##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | scientist | manager | fisherman  | electrician |
| Music-Genre   | electronic             | r&b          | folk | ambient    |

