.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, gospel, soul, disco
4 different pets are kept: ferret, mouse, rat, chinchilla
1. the fan soul is not the owner of the rat##6
2. the owner of the ferret and the fan reggae have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the mouse and the fan gospel have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the fan soul##5
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the fan disco##1
6. the fan gospel is not the owner of the mouse##6
7. the fan disco is somewhere to the left of the fan gospel##5
8. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the fan reggae##1
9. the owner of the chinchilla is not the fan disco##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | soul | disco  | gospel |
| Pet           | mouse   | ferret     | rat | chinchilla      |

