There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, japanese, polish, chinese
1. the person watching musical movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the polish is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
4. the mexican and the person watching crime movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching time-travel movies and the mexican have different parity positions##9
6. the polish is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
7. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
8. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the chinese##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | disaster | crime | time-travel |
| Nationality   | chinese        | polish    | mexican   | japanese |

