2. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's sport is baseball##2
3. the person who's sport is cycling and the fan r&b have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the fan r&b is not to the right of the fan reggae##8
6. the fan disco is somewhere to the left of the fan reggae##5
7. the fan r&b is somewhere to the right of the fan dubstep##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | disco | r&b         | reggae     |
| Sport         | parkour | cycling  | baseball | snowboarding |

