4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is not the owner of the turtle##6
6. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the owner of the pony have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
