.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, potato, raspberry, lime
There are 4 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, american
1. the person eating lime is not the american##6
2. the american is not to the right of the british##8
3. the person eating raspberry is not to the left of the person eating lime##8
4. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
5. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
6. the american is on the far left##1
7. the british is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
8. the person eating cherry is the egyptian##1
9. the person eating lime and the british have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | potato   | lime    | raspberry | cherry    |
| Nationality   | american | british | indonesian   | egyptian |

