2. the fan trance is not to the left of the person eating lettuce##8
3. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere between the fan metal and the fan trance##7
4. the fan trance is somewhere between the fan pop and the person eating pumpkin##7
5. the fan techno is not the person eating artichoke##6
6. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
7. the person eating strawberry is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | artichoke | pumpkin | lettuce | strawberry  |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | techno | trance | pop |

