2. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
6. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
8. the person watching adventure movies and the person drinking cola have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching western movies and the person drinking milk have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | mirinda  | milk  | cola |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | western | epic | adventure      |

