.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, soy-milk, water, fanta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, indie, hip-hop, techno
 1. the person drinking soy-milk and the fan hip-hop have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
 3. the fan trance is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking sprite##7
 4. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 5. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan hip-hop is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
 7. the person drinking fanta and the fan indie have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the fan techno##3
 9. the fan techno is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the fan trance##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | fanta | water  | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre   | techno | hip-hop     | trance | indie     |

