The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, hiking, gardening, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the person drinking tea and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite    | tea | fanta | coffee |
| Hobby      | gardening | magic-tricks   | hiking   | collecting   |

