.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, hot-chocolate, milk, 7up
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, sudoku, gardening
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
 4. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 6. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
 7. the person drinking 7up and the person who's hobby is drawing have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
 9. the person drinking 7up is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is drawing have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | milk        | 7up   | sprite      |
| Hobby      | gardening | sudoku | drawing | cooking |

 